        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3657086177" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16222321791887766637">I should know by now that bringing a Roth novel on vacation and casually picking it up does a disservice to the book. The Anatomy Lesson is essentially an examination of Zuckerman’s midlife crisis and despite the strong writing, I didn’t connect to this one as much as it’s predecessors. Blame me, not Roth for that. Looking forward to continuing my Roth journey in the new year. 3.5/5</span>

          </span>
